{"name":"Soothing Scents","type":"spell","img":"beneos_assets/beneos_spells/0003_soothing_scents/soothing_scents-icon.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<h1>Spell Description</h1><p>You exude a comforting smell, capable of bolstering a creatures spiritual and physical fortitude.</p><p>Creatures within a <strong>15-feet-radius</strong> centered on yourself gain a number of <strong>temporary hit points equal to your spellcasting ability modifier</strong> and can use their reaction to <strong>repeat one initial saving throw against a condition they are afflicted with</strong>, ending the condition on a success. They have advantage on this saving throw.</p><p></p><h1>Spell Card</h1><img src=\"beneos_assets/beneos_spells/0003_soothing_scents/soothing_scents-front.webp\" class=\" centered\" width=\"400\" height=\"575\" /><img src=\"beneos_assets/beneos_spells/spell_card_back.webp\" class=\" centered\" width=\"400\" height=\"575\" />","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Beneos","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"8","units":"inst"},"cover":null,"crewed":false,"target":{"value":15,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["@mod","temphp"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":3,"school":"con","components":{"vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"A fragrant flower","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"effects":[],"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"0184cd3a8585874702b71d07c5e1a67b76e01a27","sourceId":"Item.X8qa2vhmG5hsmuDe"},"core":{},"exportSource