{"name":"Grove Moss","type":"spell","img":"beneos_assets/beneos_spells/0001_grove_moss/grove_moss-icon.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<h1>Spell Description</h1><p>Upon casting this spell, soft, magical moss sprouts from the ground centered on yourself. This moss exudes a calming earthy smell and is as soft as a feather bed, giving warmth when it is cold or have a gentle cooling effect when it is hot.</p><p></p><p>After finishing a long rest, a creature that has rested on the moss gains 1D8 temporary hit points and gains advantage on the first ability check made after resting. The moss vanishes after eight hours, leaving behind only a faint scent and the vague memories of pleasant dreams.</p><p></p><p><strong>At Higher Levels:</strong> When you this spell using a spell of 2nd level or higher, the amount of temporary hit points increases ba 1D8 for every two slot levels above the first.</p><p></p><h1>Spell Card</h1><img src=\"beneos_assets/beneos_spells/0001_grove_moss/grove_moss-front.webp\" class=\"centered\" width=\"400\" height=\"575\" /><img src=\"beneos_assets/beneos_spells/spell_card_back.webp\" class=\"centered\" width=\"400\" height=\"575\" />","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Beneos","activation":{"type":"minute","cost":10,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"8","units":"hour"},"cover":null,"crewed":false,"target":{"value":15,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"sphere"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"con","components":{"vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"a Pinch of fertile soil","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mo